/*
 * ================================================================
 * ANAEROBIC DIGESTER - TANK 1 - LQR OBSERVER CONTROLLER
 * Arduino GIGA R1 WiFi
 * 
 * Replaces cyclic pH hold with:
 *   Phase 1: P-control to stabilize pH into [6.5, 8.0]
 *   Phase 2: Luenberger Observer + LQR optimal control
 *             Targets: ORP ≈ -173 mV, MFC ≈ 401 mV
 * 
 * Same hardware as stress test code:
 *   Sensors: pH (A0), ORP (A1), EC (A2), MFC (A3), Temp (D10)
 *   Pumps:   Urine (D8), Kombucha/Phosphoric (D2), Acetate (D4)
 *   MFC Gate Relay: D3
 *   Arduino IoT Cloud: 14 variables
 * 
 * Model: 4-state discrete-time (1-min steps)
 *   States:  [EC, pH, h1(VFA), h2(microbial)]
 *   Inputs:  [urine, acetate, phosphoric] (mL/dose)
 *   Outputs: [ORP, MFC] (mV, predicted)
 * ================================================================
 */

